Gunmen have abducted Hon. Justice Nwosu Iheme of the Court Of Appeal, Benin City, Edo State. Her abductors attacked her SUV vehicle along Benin-Agbor road near Christ Choosen Church, killed her police orderly before taking her away according to eye witnesses. A witness told Crime News that a Toyota Voltron car with four armed men accosted her vehicle and immediately opened fire, forcing forcing the driver to stop. The Publicity Secretary of NBA Benin, Douglas Ogbankwa has confirmed the incident.